lead_paragraph: Even though they let a win get away Wednesday night, the Boston Red Sox locked up something more important. And as far as they were concerned, an AL East title was certainly worth celebrating.

headline.print_headline: Boston Red Sox Clinch AL East Crown, Go Worst to 1st Again
